en_121238_0	We heard many heart rendering stories from around the Island where parents are ill-treated by the children.
en_121238_1	The Meetiyagoda police were able to find a woman locked in a bathroom adjoining a toilet which was under construction.
en_121238_2	The woman had been locked in the bathroom by her granddaughter.
en_121238_3	The 78 year old mother was in a house situated at Mudyanse-watte area in Meetiyagoda, Kaluwarabeddara area.Â  She has three children while one of her daughter is abroad.
en_121238_4	The daughter who was abroad is the one who has locked the mother in an unsafe bathroom in this manner.
en_121238_5	The bathroom which did not have a door had a makeshift door made out with few rods of ion.
en_121238_6	The ion rod door was locked with a padlock to make sure the woman could not come out.
en_121238_7	The police found the woman in the bathroom on information received.
en_121238_8	And the police arrested the granddaughter for insecurely lodging the woman.
en_121238_9	The police also called another daughter of the old woman, over to the place and have arrested her as well for not taking care of her mother properly.
